how many defenders of the faith are here tonight the sentinel along deserted avenues steam begins to rise the figures primed and ready prepared for quick surprise he's watching for a sign his life is on the line dogs whine in the alleys smoke is on the wind from deep inside its empty shell a cathedral bell begins ringing out its toll a storm begins to grow amidst the upturned burned out cars the challengers await and in their fists clutch iron bars with which to seal his fate across his chest in scabbards rest the rows of throwing knives whose razor points in challenged tests have finished many lives now facing as another the stand off eats at time then all at once a silence falls as the bell ceases its chime upon this sign the challengers with shrieks and cries rush forth the knives fly out like bullets upon their deadly course screams of pain and agony rent the silent air amidst the dying bodies blood runs everywhere the figure stands expressionless impassive and alone unmoved by this victory and the seeds of death he's sown sworn to avenge condemn to hell tempt not the blade all fear the sentinel wow no one really does read the details judas priest defenders of the faith the song the sentinel you're right not everyone reads all the details or else they are not judas priest fans Sin City The Amber Spyglass Judas Priest Shaggy dog story Similarities between the Bible and the Qur'an Professional wrestling throws Professional wrestling match types Timeline of heavy metal Professional wrestling holds The Lion, the Witch and the Wardrobe Kain (Legacy of Kain) Piccolo Junior Saga Professional wrestling attacks Blood (computer game) Eastern Orthodox Church Luminoth Sub-Zero YuYu Hakusho Imperial Guard (Warhammer 40,000 army) Characters of Naruto Ayyavazhi mythology Columbine High School massacre Fist of the North Star Kill Bill Trench warfare Professional wrestling aerial techniques Scorpion (Mortal Kombat) Escape from New York Seppuku Locations in the Warcraft Universe 